### AbacatePay Webhook - Billing Paid Event
### 
### IMPORTANT NOTES:
### 1. Query Parameter: webhookSecret=tomate-header (for basic auth)
### 2. Header: x-webhook-signature (HMAC-SHA256 signature - REQUIRED by controller)
### 3. Header: x-webhook-secret (optional - you mentioned this in your request)
###
### To generate the HMAC signature:
### Option 1 (Recommended): Use the helper script
###   cd backend/https/payment
###   node generate-webhook-signature.js
###   Copy the generated signature and replace REPLACE_WITH_HMAC_SIGNATURE below
###
### Option 2: Manual calculation
###   - Use the AbacatePay public key (defined in webhook.service.ts)
###   - Calculate: HMAC-SHA256(body, publicKey) in base64
###   - Example in Node.js:
###     const crypto = require('crypto');
###     const signature = crypto.createHmac('sha256', PUBLIC_KEY).update(JSON.stringify(body)).digest('base64');
###
### Note: For local testing, you may want to temporarily disable signature verification 
###       in webhook.controller.ts by commenting out the HMAC verification check

POST http://localhost:8080/v1/webhooks/abacatepay?webhookSecret=tomate-header
Content-Type: application/json
x-webhook-signature: +vJ/oS+hfLRVc9PgZHRj890bFYpvUlXED+Nxmf8YIkY=
x-webhook-secret: tomate-header

